MB tab
	- filters (a la item search plugin)
		- patch filter
	- colour items based on being in favourites/history and show filter type as an icon next to names
Retainers tab
	- inventory view, ability to manipulate and list from there
Listings tab

misc features
	- turret mode: keep all listings for current character up to date by periodically checking local listings
	- autoretainer mode: OnPostVenture update any listings (auto add retainer listings to a ToCache list)
	- contextmenu to view items on the mb or list them for sale
	- price watch list/auto buy